<paragraph id="523C478F525A6E7565115701661740DF" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
BRAZIL. Pernambuco, Agrestina, Inselberg Pedra 
<normalizedToken id="93079F827307C98FA4A37289CB6A62FA" originalValue="Cabeça">Cabeca</normalizedToken>
de Velho, 
<emphasis id="7FABC6741F32D579DE206F51B7129189" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">P. Gomes, M. Alves &amp; B. Maciel</emphasis>
